<div class="modal hide fade" id="loadModal">
  <div class="modal-header">
    <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" id="closeModalButton">X</button>
    <h3>Load A CSV Template</h3>
  </div>
  <div class="modal-body">
    <p>If you have utilized the LRMI CSV Template, you may select it from your local folder. The file must be in CSV format to be uploaded.</p>
    <p>You may find a copy of the <a href="Tagger CSV Upload Template User Instructions.docx">LRMI Template Guide</a> available online.This file contains the CSV file embedded.</p>
    <p>If you'd like more details on how the LRMI specification for each data field please see the appendix in the help file "importing resource data to create tags through bulk processing."</p>

    <form id="fileForm">
        <input type="file" id="files" name="files" multiple />
    </form>

    <hr/>
    <h4>Quick Load</h4>
    <p>To create multiple entries enter <i>title,URL</i> once per line.<br/>   <strong>Example:</strong><br/>  Actual Title,http://www.test.com<br/>Actual Title Two,http://www.test2.com</p>

    <textarea id="loadModalTextArea" style="height: 40px; width: 95%;font-size:small;"></textarea>
  </div>
  <div class="modal-footer">
    <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary" data-dismiss="modal" id="saveLoadModalButton">Load</a>
  </div>
</div>
